# ─── FRONTEND ENVIRONMENT — DEVELOPMENT ────────────────────────────────────
#
# In development, leave VITE_API_BASE_URL unset (or empty).
# The Vite dev-server proxy forwards /api/* → http://localhost:5000 for you,
# which avoids CORS entirely.  api.js uses an empty baseURL automatically.
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=

